<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Attack Pages</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Launch Attack</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <p>Here you can launch attacks against specified targets. Choose the desired method and enter the details to start the attack.</p>
        <p>Available Slots: <%= slots %></p>
        <p>Max Time Allowed: <%= maxTime %> seconds</p>
        <form action="/attack" method="POST">
            <input type="text" name="host" placeholder="Target Host" required>
            <input type="number" name="time" placeholder="Time (seconds)" required>
            <select name="method" required>
                <option value="PROXY">PROXY</option>
                <option value="BYPASS">BYPASS</option>
                <option value="FLOOD">FLOOD</option>
                <option value="MIXED">MIXED</option>
            </select>
            <button type="submit">Launch Attack</button>
        </form>
        <% if (message) { %>
            <div class="message"><%= message %></div>
        <% } %>
    </main>
</body>
</html>

